</person>
 song takes a positive look at the programme. He is quoted at the beginning saying humourously: "This is what America has been longing for.. a jailhouse rock, which they only saw in Elvis... Jailhouse.. and they're rockin')".<weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wAjItY7X0Yc">
